{"tid":468081,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"傳說中既新《古惑仔》:黃金兄弟","createTime":"2017-11-14T05:32:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-15T08:05:56.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"4e637f2205b51eb4bd78dfa8f4b17007e0ee93db","tid":468081,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T05:32:31.000Z","msg":"《黃金兄弟》故事講述獅王（鄭伊健）、火山（陳小春）、淡定（錢嘉樂）、老鼠（林曉峰）、Bill（謝天華）五個出生入死的兄弟，在恩師曹sir（曾志偉）的帶領下，為了救濟兒童而偷取特效藥，卻慘遭設局，陷入槍林彈雨的險境之中。兄弟們抱著視死如歸的豪情，展開一連串的追查與激戰。他們明白，即使無法活著回來，也比一人活著痛快。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/14/133224_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F14%2F133224_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=42ea2061&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5703e4359adca09e5b43ad3b59f7e5a8634c413d","tid":468081,"uid":25601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T05:37:07.000Z","msg":"Out唔out d"},{"pid":"fa4399a542d1107818eb54f38f0105872103bfae","tid":468081,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T05:38:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6afe49236101dc29f06900b0b92af617ffd871b6","tid":468081,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T05:39:33.000Z","msg":"炒夠冷飯未？"},{"pid":"013f1f8d37daaff1d47b83d584dd195d1eda92e2","tid":468081,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T06:08:19.000Z","msg":"蝗精？"},{"pid":"982f156dc43fc6ec683f74a8f2b0df71f2411f37","tid":468081,"uid":26451,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T06:49:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9a9acd744e8c09152cf89e64d50b10cb725b188b","tid":468081,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T08:09:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>劇本老撚土到</blockquote><br />\n全職大賊"},{"pid":"9a1e72c1ea9f7f22ab5656d9972b5b65ad25137